<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Van Kanaan ram pan in, Thlarau hruaimi kan si
 Abraham Moses he van holh kan hmang cang lai
 Minung nih tial chommi, lei member si loin
 Pathian thinlung chung ah, thisen ttial kan si cang.

[C1]
   Vancung member kan si, Van nun ngeitu ka si ee
   Hamcia mi mo ka si, Khrih he um dingin
   Nunnak cauk chungah, min tialmi vialte cu
   Pathian inn chungkhar ah, member tling kan si cang.

[V2]
 Kan Bawipa Jesuh nih, ka ra zau lai ati
 A mithiang lawr dingin, chum cungin a ra lai
 Cu ni kan phak tik cun, A van mithiang hna he
 Thangthat zai hlasa in, Bawi Khrih he kan leng lai.

[V3]
 Abraham Pa-Pathian, cu kan Pathian a si
 Sualman thihnak thongchung, ummi ka si lio ah
 Jesuh Khrih kan tlangbawi, thisen thawinak thawngin
 Mi luat fa ka si cang, cu biatak in ka nung.

[V4]
 Jesuh cu kan nunnak, le kan damnak a si
 Ka lung retheih caan ah, Hnemtu Bawipa a si
 Hmuh khawhmi lei ram ah, tlinglo sihmanhning law
 Hmuh khawh lonun ram ah, tling ter tu bawi ka ngei.</lyrics>
<title>VANCUNG MEMBER KAN SI</title>
</song>